messages.text: where r u? u should have been here by now
at the park. taking scooter for a quick walk.
you know my parents are gone, right?
that’s why I’m walking scooter. I won’t be coming home tonight. ;)
wut do you want from Zen Garden?
Chinese on our 6 month anniversary?? No way.
after I’m done walking scooter, I’ll pick up some real food for us
sometimes I hate how perfect you are tbh
it looks like a war vet on the swing set by himself
he’s clutching his stomach saying “make it stop, make it stop”
shit. He fell off the swing, he’s not getting up
just call the police, you can’t help him
scooter is freaked out. he won’t go near him
he’s drench in sweat and he’s smells worse than your gerbil
HIS EYES, HIS NOSE, HIS MOUTH
his arms are covered in scabs and puss
I’ve never seen any thing like this before
I just called the cops. They’ll be there soon. Get out of there
are you okay? Talk to me!
me and scooter are pretty far away now
it’s okay my shit stayed strong
babe, after that. I'm sorry I can’t do us tonight
hey, sorry again about last night, want me to give you a ride home today from school??
nah, I’m going take the bus
but you hate taking the bus
The guy from the park…he has some type of virus
that’s why you're going to take the bus?
I just think u need to get checked out
ya, I’m like superman to your lois lane
Amber is texting me that you were sweating a lot today in first period
how do you explain the nose bleeds?
I thought we were honest with each other
we are. I've never lied to you
Amber texted me you had to leave class…I was worried
I can hear the vomiting, it sounds awful
then you’ll stop being such a bitch about this
what ur hearing is your concerned girlfriend walking back to Spanish
Good and make sure you don’t tell anyone.
it’s lunch and our table is a ghost town
they’re our friends, they needed to know
you look like you’re about to pass out
Where are you!? Why aren’t you by me?
im going to principle's office…you need help
hell with all of this. I’m outta here
Cliff, where are you going? You need a doctor!
I just wanted to help you.
im worried, your parents are worried, we’re all worried
no one has seen you since you left school
I just want to know that you’re okay. I’m sorry if I was coming off like a bitch. I just care.
tell me where you are and I can call the police
I thought we loved each other?!!
is that you knocking at my door?
it's taking me all my strength to stand
don’t let me die on your doorstep
YOU NEED TO BE IN A HOSPITAL
I can hear you on the other side.
OMG IT’S COMING THRU UNDERNEATH OMG
No, the ambulance is coming, you’ll be okay.
I don’t know what’s happening to me
It feels like my skin is on fire and there isnt blood anymore just white puss
we were supposed to be together forever
you have nothing to be sorry about
No. I’m sorry that I never told you that I loved you
I opened the door and you were gone. I could see them dragging your lifeless body away
the blood is still on the porch
I thought we’d be able to withstand anything.
I’m sorry I opened the door too late, Cliff.
